- [ONS Blue Book 2025](https://www.ons.gov.uk/economy/nationalaccounts/uksectoraccounts/datasets/unitedkingdomeconomicaccounts) (UK)
- [ABS Australian National Accounts: Input-Output Tables](https://www.abs.gov.au/statistics/economy/national-accounts/australian-national-accounts-input-output-tables) (Australia)
- HMT Green Book additionality guide (2014, updated 2022)
